    <item>
      <title>哈维称股市将突破“忧虑之墙”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/stocks-will-scale-this-wall-of-worry-harvey-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行股票策略主管克里斯·哈维表示，随着美联储缓慢降息，明年股市和风险都将走高。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/stocks-will-scale-this-wall-of-worry-harvey-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙财政部长：对南方共同市场协议持乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/portugal-s-finance-minister-optimistic-on-mercosur-deal-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙财政部长 Joaquim Miranda Sarmento 告诉彭博社记者 Oliver Crook，他对欧盟与南方共同市场的贸易协议持乐观态度，称这将使消费者受益。Sarmento 还表示，葡萄牙并不担心法国政治局势带来的溢出风险，并讨论了欧盟与特朗普政府的贸易方式，并表示欧盟需要就国防资金问题达成联合解决方案。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/portugal-s-finance-minister-optimistic-on-mercosur-deal-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:28:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥本海默称利率应该下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/oppenheimer-says-interest-rates-should-be-coming-down-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席全球股票策略师彼得·奥本海默 (Peter Oppenheimer) 谈论了美国货币政策的走向、股市在此次降息周期中的表现、市场回报为何应该扩大以及即将上任的特朗普政府提高关税将如何影响市场。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/oppenheimer-says-interest-rates-should-be-coming-down-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:17:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
